                <td> <p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="1"><i><br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">
                    The </kw><a href="http://www.worldbank.org/oed"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Independent Evaluation Group (IEG)</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1"> is an independent unit within the World 
                    Bank; it reports directly to the Bank's Board of Executive 
                    Directors. The goals of IEG 's evaluations are to draw lessons 
                    from Bank experience, and to provide an objective basis for 
                    assessing the results of the Bank's work.</kw></i></font></p>
